<PART ID=tocexecenv>
<TITLE>Execution Environment</TITLE>

<CHAPTER id=execenv>
<TITLE>File System Hierarchy</TITLE>

<PARA>
The <filename>/proc</filename> directory need not be present.
</PARA>

<PARA>
The directory <filename>/opt/provider/package/</filename> is added to 
the <filename>/opt/package/</filename> diretory specified by the FHS v2.2 
in section 3.12, where <filename>provider</filename> is the LANANA registered 
provider name. 
<FOOTNOTE>
<PARA>
This would allow possible large collection of applications by 
certain providers to organize under their reserved /opt/ subdirectory
such as <filename>/opt/acme/lsb-bricks</filename> instead of
<filename>/opt/lsb-acme-bricks</filename>.
</PARA>
</FOOTNOTE>
</PARA>

</CHAPTER>

</PART>
